item.title: You Won't Believe What Happened When Blackpink and BTS Collided on How You Like That!
item.description: Introduction The world of K-pop has been electrified with the collaboration between two of its biggest stars: Blackpink and BTS. On June 26th, 2020, the two groups released the music video for their single, “How You Like That.” This collaboration has been highly anticipated and has already made a huge impact on the K-pop industry. Background Information on Blackpink and BTS Blackpink is a four-member South Korean girl group that debuted in 2016.
